# Runtime-uploaded knowledge package assets (services/asset_ingestion.py
# writes to assets/<package_id>/<asset_id>_<filename> -- config.ASSETS_DIR).
# Test runs and local dev sessions populate these as a side effect of
# ingesting packages; they are never meant to be version-controlled.
# This pattern only matches subdirectories of assets/, so the brand
# logo files committed directly in assets/ (kt_logo.png, kt_logo.svg,
# kt_logo_icon.png, kt_logo_cube.png) are unaffected.
assets/*/
